  "description": "This mod adds classic Spanish omelette and a beetroot version, along with a craftable frying pan as a weapon.",
  "body": "<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/S300mZWL/images/1779aa964762ab03f4ffc36689c50be48449428e.png\" alt=\"Logo\"></img>\n\n<h1>What is it about?</h1>\n\nThis mod introduces two variations of the famous Spanish omelette: the classic potato omelette and a version with beetroot. Additionally, you'll be able to craft a frying pan that can be used as a weapon.\n\n<h1>Content</h1>\n\n+ 4 foods\n\n+ 1 weapon\n\n<h1>Recipies</h1>\n\nTortilla recipe\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/S300mZWL/images/2b042d52452c344a26a4408e17e02538813844cd.png\" alt=\"Tortilla recipe\"></img>\n\nTortilla with beetroot recipe\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/S300mZWL/images/708d12001b9f9ccdf5b6ac2d589f9e08f5fb4c72.png\" alt=\"Tortilla with beetroot recipe\"></img>\n\nTortilla sandwich recipe\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/S300mZWL/images/fc48312baf72c1cd704d0e47defa39e7e394ff1b.png\" alt=\"Tortilla sandwich recipe\"></img>\n\nTortilla slice recipe\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/S300mZWL/images/fe7a9c6febdc91318da29a04689e23bb0475b781.png\" alt=\"Tortilla slice recipe\"></img>\n\nFrying pan recipe\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/S300mZWL/images/f09cb7d7d4eaab395ad8b45cc907e40324ef1667.png\" alt=\"Frying pan recipe\"></img>",
